awp_snow_fort

This is a medium sized awp map with 4 levels.  Each team spawns on opposite sides of the map, and everything is symmetrical.  

All players start with the following equipment:  Awp sniper rifle, Deagle pistol, knife, kevlar vest.

Please downaload, comment and enjoy!

Happy Sniping!

-	48 Spawns, 24 per a team
-	Nav file for bots
-	Overview radar map
-	Cube Maps
-	3d Skybox
-	Optimized with No Draw for better FPS
-	Everything is packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat
-	Custom Skybox by Karatek√§fer
